        .dashed-separator
        Tor prevents people from learning your location or browsing habits.
        %br
        %button.btn DOWNLOAD TOR
        %br
        %a(href="#") Learn more!
        .thin-separator
    .row
      .spacer-2
      %a(href="#more-windows-linux") &#9660; More for Windows 
      .spacer-2
      .thin-separator

  #gnu-linux.text-center
    .row
      %h2 GNU/Linux 
      %p
        GNU/Linux users probably have these tools already. 
        If not, install them with your package manager!
    .row
      .col-sm-3.col-sm-offset-3.vertical-separated
        %img(src="images/pidgin-logo.png")
        %h3 Pidgin
        .dashed-separator
        Encrypted chats for Facebook, Google, Duck Duck Go, and more.
        %br
        %button.btn DOWNLOAD PIDGIN 
        %br
        %a(href="#") Learn more!
        .thin-separator
      .col-sm-3
        %img(src="images/tor-logo.png")
        %h3 Tor
        .dashed-separator
        Tor prevents people from learning your location or browsing habits.
        %br
        %button.btn DOWNLOAD TOR
        %br
        %a(href="#") Learn more!
        .thin-separator
    .row
      .spacer-2
      %a(href="#more-windows-linux") &#9660; More for GNU/Linux 
      .spacer-2
  #more
    .row
      %h3.text-center#more-android More for Android
      .carat-separator
      %ol
        %li {Encrypt your phone} and choose a 10 digit PIN, to for very strong protection if your phone is lost, stolen, or seized.
        %li {Firefox} syncs your passwords securely, and lets you install privacy-protecting extensions like {Adblock Plus}, {Noscript}, and {HTTPS Everywhere}.
        %li {Orbot} and {Orweb} let you browse the web privately and anonymously with Tor.
        %li For savvy users, {K-9} and {APG} let you send encrypted emails.
    .row
      %h3.text-center#more-iphone More for Iphone
      .carat-separator
      %ol
        %li According to Apple’s {Legal Process Guidelines}, Facetime calls and iMessages are end-to-end encrypted. This is significant, but Textsecure and Redphone are more secure and trustworthy
        %li Use a PIN on your iPhone for better legal protection against searches, and some protection against thieves.
    .row
      %h3.text-center#more-mac More for Mac
      .carat-separator
      %ol
        %li Filevault is built-in, and protects you if your Mac is lost, stolen, or sized. {Turn on Filevault.}
        %li {GPG tools} lets you encrypt emails using Apple’s Mail.app
    .row
      %h3.text-center#more-windows-linux More for Windows and GNU/Linux
      .carat-separator
      %ol
        %li {Firefox} syncs your passwords securely, and lets you install privacy-protecting extensions like {Adblock Plus}, {Noscript}, and {HTTPS Everywhere}.
        %li For savvy users, {Thunderbird} and {Enigmail} let you encrypt your emails.
        %li GNU/Linux users, install all these tools from your favorite package manager.



